{
  "texts": [
    "The recall is the number of positives recognised and correctly categorised among all positive classes and is reported appropriately.",
    "The precision is defined as the number of positives identified and correctly classified as actual positives.",
    "The F-Measure is computed using the model's precision and recall harmonic means.",
    "It is worth mentioning that an F-measure of 1 is frequently obtained for a flawless model.",
    "This metric is expressed as follows:TP TN Accuracy P N ´Çź ´ÇŻ ´Çź(1)Pr TP ecision TP FP ´ÇŻ ´Çź (2) Re () TP call TPR TP FN ´ÇŻ ´Çź (3) FP FPR FP TN ´ÇŻ ´Çź (4) 2 Pr Re Pr Re ecision call F Measure ecision call ´é┤ ´é┤ ´Çş ´ÇŻ ´Çź(5) Experimental ResultsWhen performing preprocessing of the image, the performance of eight different machine learning image feature extractors such as Auto colour, Binary filter, Edge Detection, Fuzzy Color Texture Histogram Filter (FCTH), J-PEG Color, Gabor filter, Pyramid of Gradients (PHOG), and Simple Color filter is investigated."
